3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Lilac%20Chaser%20is%20perhaps%20my%20favorite%20illusion%20of%20all%20time%2C%20largely%20because%20it%20combines%20so%20many%20different%20illusions%20into%20one%20amazing%20piece.%20It%20was%20first%20built%20by%20Jeremy%20Hinton%20in%202005%2C%20and%20has%20made%20the%20internet%20rounds%20many%20times!%20To%20get%20this%20thing%20going%20all%20you%20really%20need%20to%20do%20is%20focus%20on%20the%20dot%20in%20the%20center%2C%20the%20rest%20should%20hit%20you%20one%20effect%20after%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22desktop-ad%22%3E%3Cdiv%20data-pw-desk%3D%22leaderboard_btf%22%20id%3D%22pwDeskLbBtf1%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20effect%20I%20observe%20is%20the%20afterimage%20effect%2C%20whereby%20the%20empty%20hole%20in%20the%20circle%20suddenly%20gives%20you%20a%20circle%20of%20the%20inverted%20color%2C%20so%20at%20its%20initial%20settings%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20green%20circle%E2%80%A6%20that%20alone%20is%20amazing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20get%20hit%20by%20the%20Troxler%20Fade%2C%20whereby%20the%20gradient%20circles%20should%20suddenly%20disappear.%20Often%20for%20me%2C%20it%20is%20as%20though%20the%20green%20circle%20eats%20them%20up%20and%20they%E2%80%99re%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20of%20all%20things%2C%20the%20green%20circle%20will%20keep%20circling%E2%80%A6%20if%20you%20stare%20that%20this%20for%20a%20really%20long%20time%2C%20and%20then%20look%20away%20you%E2%80%99ll%20still%20be%20seeing%20green%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20incredible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20To%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Here%20you%20can%20mix%20up%20the%20colors%2C%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20dots%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20able%20to%20see%20that%20the%20inverse%20disc%20can%20more%20or%20less%20show%20you%20the%20full%20gamut%20of%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20id%3D%22cites-and-extras%22%3ECites%20and%20Extras%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%5B1%5D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2F